Usage: convertFenceToBlackBox [-help] [-noRebuildTiming] [-size {x y}] { -cell <string> | -hinst <string> }

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # Specifies name of the partition. (string, optional)
-hinst <string>    # Specifies name of the hinst. (string, optional)
-noRebuildTiming   # Skips re-building the time graph and re-initializing the
                   # top cell information. (bool, optional)
-size {x y}        # Specifies the width and height of the blackbox. 
                   # (point, optional)